nodes.text: Norlin Wennen was a male Human and the father of Republic Treasury Audit Division Besany Wennen. When Besany was ten years old, Norlin's wife left them sometime after their vacation to the jewel-caves of Birsingrial. Norlin almost remarried but the plan did not push through, much to the relief of Besany, who had trouble liking her almost stepsister. Norlin died in a medcenter before the Clone Wars started.
